column5: Please help me out by voting for a picture (fishing related) i have entered in a contest, i am currently in 2nd place. If i can move into 1st by this Friday i can win a moosehead muskoka chair. I am a really big fan of moosehead beer and would love to win the chair. I have voted for alot of other people's contests on here so now is your chance to help me out! Here is the link with instrutions on how to vote, you must click LIKE on the moosehead page and LIKE the picture i posted of all the perch. Every vote will be greatly appreciated!  http://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=749961152#!/event.php?eid=111445615605497
Thanks for the votes i am only 37 votes behind the leader

Thanks guys I am only 20 votes from the leader now, i see this is getting lots of views but most are not taking the 30 seconds to vote Voting ends this Friday, please vote if you can and help a fellow fisherman out!
just an update the vote is close and tomorrow is the final day for voting! will be sure to post pics of the chair if i end up pulling this off.
Did you send Canadadude a PM yet to vote for you??  Good luck with the chair....
